Package: toposort
Title: Topological Sorting Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Taras", "Zakharko", , "taras.zakharko@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7601-8424"))
Description: Flexible and ergonomic topological sorting implementation for R. Supports a variety
  of input data encoding (lists of edges or adjacency matrices, graphs edge direction, item indices 
  or item labels), stable sort variants as well as cycle detection with detailed diagnostics. 
